  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiple upload sources (local, URL, camera, Dropbox, Google Drive)",
    "Large file handling with chunking and resumable uploads",
    "Built-in image editor with cropping, filters, and transformations",
    "Customizable appearance with CSS and pre-built themes",
    "Framework-agnostic Web Components",
    "TypeScript support with full type definitions",
    "Localization support for 30+ languages",
    "File validation and secure uploads",
